      <title>纳格尔说，德国需要改革以及更高的支出。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-needs-reforms-as-well-as-higher-spending-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国民总裁约阿希姆·纳格尔（Joachim Nagel）说，德国经济需要进行改革来提高增长潜力和竞争力，并且不得依靠更高的支出从多年停滞中挽救它。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-needs-reforms-as-well-as-higher-spending-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>四年后，印度斯坦锌重返卢比债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/hindustan-zinc-to-return-to-rupee-bond-market-after-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度斯坦锌有限公司（Hindustan Zinc Ltd.）周一清除了一项提议，要求通过债券筹集多达50亿卢比（5730万美元），这将是大亨阿尼尔·阿加瓦尔（Tycoon Anil Agarwal）领导的公司在至少四年内首次发行的本地货币发行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/hindustan-zinc-to-return-to-rupee-bond-market-after-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国信贷风险随着关税而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/us-credit-risk-rises-as-tariffs-job-cuts-stoke-recession-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一上午，美国的仪表今年表现出最高的信用风险，因为投资者根据关税并削减了联邦劳动力，对该国经济状况表现出新的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/us-credit-risk-rises-as-tariffs-job-cuts-stoke-recession-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 12:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普过渡谈话燃烧衰退焦虑时，国库会获得</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/treasuries-gain-as-trump-transition-talk-fuels-recession-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普总统周日的评论，美国经济正面临“过渡时期”，这是因为经济放缓可能在拐角处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/treasuries-gain-as-trump-transition-talk-fuels-recession-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 09:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战略家看到更多的S＆amp; P 500波动性随着关税的担忧而开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-warns-s-p-500-to-sink-5-on-growth-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街战略家的合唱团警告说，股票市场上的波动性上升，摩根士丹利的迈克尔·威尔逊（Michael Wilson）的最新声音在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的贸易大战中发出了有关经济增长的警报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-warns-s-p-500-to-sink-5-on-growth-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 08:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
