      <title>J. Safra Sarasin以10亿欧元的交易购买萨克斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/swiss-private-bank-j-safra-sarasin-to-buy-70-in-denmark-s-saxo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士财富经理银行J. Safra Sarasin同意在近年来最大的私人银行交易之一中购买丹麦萨克斯银行A/S的70％。]]></description>
