    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉警告规则，可能会变成类似于公平的sukuk</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/fitch-cautions-on-rule-that-could-make-sukuk-similar-to-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉伊斯兰财务负责人巴沙尔·纳托尔（Bashar Al Natoor）表示，拟议的对全球苏武士政权的变更有可能将资产类别转变为类似股票的工具，该工具无法由信用评级公司评估。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/fitch-cautions-on-rule-that-could-make-sukuk-similar-to-equity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 06:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ServiceNow接近交易以购买AI助理制造商MoveWorks</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/servicenow-nears-deal-to-buy-ai-assistant-maker-moveworks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ServiceNow Inc.已同意以28.5亿美元的价格购买人工智能公司MoveWorks，这是其进入AI工具的一部分，可以在不监督的情况下完成任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/servicenow-nears-deal-to-buy-ai-assistant-maker-moveworks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者将印度尼西亚的股票转储为Prabowo弯曲市场肌肉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/investors-dump-indonesia-stocks-as-prabowo-flexes-market-muscles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚公司景观中史无前例的权力积累正在加剧投资者对东南亚最大股票市场的政治影响力和透明度的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/investors-dump-indonesia-stocks-as-prabowo-flexes-market-muscles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济恐惧刺激飞往债券的飞行：市场包裹的股票袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球最大经济体的关税和政府解雇会在全球市场上延长三周的波动性。随着华尔街的预测者恢复看涨的看法，美国股票期货下跌，而对经济衰退的需求促进了美国和欧洲的主权债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 21:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
